      <title>7 月份英国公投猜测推动英镑波动性上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/pound-volatility-seen-rising-amid-speculation-of-uk-vote-in-july</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于猜测英国将比普遍预期提前举行大选，衡量英镑预期波动的一项指标大幅上涨。]]></description>
